Package aima.core.search.csp.examples

Class MapCSP

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.search.csp.CSP
      • aima.core.search.csp.examples.MapCSP
  • public class MapCSP
extends CSP
    Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (3rd Ed.): Figure 6.1, Page 204.

    The principal states and territories of Australia. Coloring this map can be viewed as a constraint satisfaction problem (CSP). The goal is to assign colors to each region so that no neighboring regions have the same color.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde, Mike Stampone
